794
00:29:54,880 --> 00:29:55,280
Tidak.

795
00:29:55,280 --> 00:29:56,199
Sudah tidak berhubungan lagi.

796
00:29:56,199 --> 00:29:57,400
Alasanku tidak menginginkan

797
00:29:57,400 --> 00:29:58,359
